                            <comment id="235821" author="adilger" created="Mon, 29 Oct 2018 17:43:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Closing this as a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11488&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_133b: @@@@@@ FAIL: OST got STATFS &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11488&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11488&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="235469" author="adilger" created="Thu, 25 Oct 2018 05:05:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Maybe you are confusing &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11488&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_133b: @@@@@@ FAIL: OST got STATFS &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11488&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11488&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;sanity test_133b: @@@@@@ FAIL: OST got STATFS&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; with &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11375&quot; title=&quot;Client 2.10 fails to mount Server 2.11.54&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11375&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11375&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;Client 2.10 fails to mount Server 2.11.54&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;?  There is nothing in this ticket that is different from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11488&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_133b: @@@@@@ FAIL: OST got STATFS &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11488&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11488&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, except that ticket is being used for a few weeks already for the &quot;OST got STATFS&quot; error, so it isn&apos;t clear to me what the benefit is of opening a second &quot;OST got STATFS&quot; ticket. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="235468" author="bzzz" created="Thu, 25 Oct 2018 04:55:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this is the same test formally, but actually it&apos;s a new verification In 133b added specifically for aggregated statfs functionality. so a different issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="235460" author="adilger" created="Thu, 25 Oct 2018 01:46:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It isn&apos;t clear why this new bug was filed?  It is essentially the same as &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11488&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_133b: @@@@@@ FAIL: OST got STATFS &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11488&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11488&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and should probably be closed as a duplicate?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
